snippet.title: Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U 2 - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
The mod is out! https://drive.google.com/drive/u/2/folders/12pAcqt93Jw2dAm2NU0Mkf5YjOaU6Ck2d

Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U 2 is a mod of NSMBU which was intended to release on December 17th but has instead been pushed to 2022.

This mod will contain:
- 40+ brand new unique levels
- Over 100 new and revamped tilesets
- Retextures and remodels of NSMBU's original assets
- A brand new soundtrack with both original and remixed music

Check out Pokestir's amazing remix used in this trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A_agcsq4kgM
